    "Durability meta dialed back: tower, inhibitor, minion, and jungle monster health/damage increased across the board to make pushing and objective trades slower and more deliberate (e.g. Outer Tower 5000->5800 HP, Inner 4000->5000, Inhibitor 3800->4500; Super Minion HP 1600-4820->1600-5240 but its damage to inhibitors/core reduced).",
